WEBVTT

14:24.830 --> 14:27.490 line:80%
Changyu can barely
feed herself and her sister.

14:27.640 --> 14:29.310 line:80%
What is she thinking,
bringing a strange man home?

14:29.310 --> 14:31.160 line:80%
Why didn't you stop her?

14:32.590 --> 14:33.800 line:80%
Look at that face,

14:33.800 --> 14:34.710 line:80%
and you'll know why.
